  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd3\u0da9\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dc0 \u0dbb\u0dd4 7500\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rs 7500 per month to affected families",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government has put in place plans to support people affected by the economic crisis, where access to food, fuel and gas has become a challenge.",
        "Accordingly, the government has planned to provide an allowance of 7500 rupees to those affected by the crisis from this month, says Mr. Ramesh Pathirana, Minister of Plantations.",
        "The grant is funded by international donor agencies. A part of the 200 million dollars of the World Bank (WB) and a part of the 200 million dollars of the Asian Development Bank (ADB) are to be allocated for this purpose.",
        "Samurdhi beneficiaries, senior citizens and medically related persons are among those eligible for the stipend."
      ],
